A mụrụ Adaora na Windsor, CT ma mgbe ọ dị afọ isii ọ kwagara n'obodo nna ya na Naịjirịa
Ọ nọrọ ihe dị ka afọ iri na Naijiria na-amụta banyere ọdịbendị ha na ụzọ ndụ ha
Mgbe ọ laghachiri Connecticut, onye na-enyocha ihe nlereanya John Casablancas, Tina Kiniry, bịakwutere ya, ọrụ ya malitere.
N'afọ puku abụọ na asaa, Akubilo pụtara na NBC dị ka otu n'ime ndị ikpeazụ iri na abụọ na Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Model Search
N'afọ puku abụọ iri na abụọ, Adaora gara ajụjụ ọnụ na Sports Illustrated na ụlọ ọrụ ime ihe ngosi obodo ya, John Casablancas
A nabatara ya ka ọ pụta na ihe ngosi ahụ wee gaa Los Angeles iji gbaa Sports Illustrated TV Show

Ọ gara n'ihu na-apụta na n'afọ puku abụọ iri na abụọ rue afọ puku abụọ iri na atọ Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Editions. Ọrụ ya gụnyekwara mkpọsa maka Covergirl, Garnier Nutrisse, House of Dereon, Ray Ban, Boden, Abercrombie, Mary Kay, Ulta, Burts Bees, na Avon
Ọ bịanyere aka ugbu a na New York Model Management.
